{"chapters": {"parte01-a-transformacao-e-o-trabalho": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">DIE VERWANDLUNG (1915)</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">A</span> <span class=\"bd\">METAMORFOSE</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Franz Kafka</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">A METAMORFOSE</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PARTE I: A Transformação e o Trabalho</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">O Absurdo Sem Explicação</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">A</span> metamorfose é dada na primeira frase — sem causa, diagnóstico ou tentativa de cura. O leitor (e o próprio Gregor) trata o impossível como <strong>problema logístico</strong>: o trem perdido, o chefe à porta.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Como aplicar</div><div class=\"tipbody\">note quando um sistema absorve o absurdo como rotina — esse é o efeito kafkiano.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">A METAMORFOSE</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PARTE I: A Transformação e o Trabalho</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">O Provedor-Máquina</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">G</span>regor sustenta pai, mãe e irmã e vive em função do dever, não de si. O emprego de caixeiro-viajante é um cárcere: viagens sem fim, contatos passageiros, medo do patrão. <strong>Sua identidade está soldada ao papel de provedor.</strong></p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Para refletir</div><div class=\"tipbody\">sem a função, o lugar dele na família evapora.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">A METAMORFOSE</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PARTE I: A Transformação e o Trabalho</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">A Engrenagem Burocrática</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">A</span>o primeiro atraso, o gerente da firma aparece <em>em pessoa</em> — a suspeita corporativa é instantânea. O indivíduo é sempre menor que o sistema impessoal que o cerca.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Modelo mental</div><div class=\"tipbody\">o gerente é a voz do sistema; foge horrorizado e sela a perda do emprego.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>04</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">4</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">A METAMORFOSE</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PARTE I: A Transformação e o Trabalho</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">A Porta e a Primeira Ferida</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">G</span>regor abre a porta com as mandíbulas e se mostra; o pânico é geral. O pai o empurra de volta ao quarto com bengala e jornal, <strong>ferindo-o no vão da porta</strong> — primeira ferida de uma série. A porta vira a medida da exclusão.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Símbolo</div><div class=\"tipbody\">a porta é a fronteira entre o humano (a sala) e o exilado (o quarto).</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "parte02-adaptacao-e-a-maca": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">DIE VERWANDLUNG (1915)</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">A</span> <span class=\"bd\">METAMORFOSE</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Franz Kafka</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">A METAMORFOSE</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PARTE II: Adaptação e a Maçã</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Corpo × Humanidade</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">G</span>regor adquire hábitos de bicho (rasteja pelas paredes, prefere comida estragada), mas conserva memória, afeto e vergonha. <strong>Por dentro, segue humano; por fora, é repugnante.</strong> A consciência resiste enquanto o corpo a trai.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Para refletir</div><div class=\"tipbody\">o que define o humano — a aparência que os outros veem ou a consciência que ninguém alcança?</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">A METAMORFOSE</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PARTE II: Adaptação e a Maçã</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">A Inversão Começa</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">C</span>ada membro da família reassume uma função produtiva. O pai renasce como autoridade fardada e vigorosa; a mãe costura; Grete cuida do quarto. <strong>Gregor, antes o eixo, vira peso morto.</strong></p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Modelo mental</div><div class=\"tipbody\">a energia vital é uma só e migra — da família para Gregor (antes), de Gregor para a família (agora).</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">A METAMORFOSE</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PARTE II: Adaptação e a Maçã</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Os Móveis e o Retrato</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">M</span>ãe e Grete tentam esvaziar o quarto para Gregor rastejar — sem ver que arrancam dele os <strong>últimos vestígios do humano</strong>. Ele se lança sobre o retrato da dama de peles e o cobre com o corpo: não deixará que o levem.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Símbolo</div><div class=\"tipbody\">esvaziar o quarto = transformá-lo em jaula nua, apagar o homem que Gregor foi.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>04</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">4</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">A METAMORFOSE</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PARTE II: Adaptação e a Maçã</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">A Maçã Encravada</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">O</span> pai chega do trabalho, interpreta a cena como ataque e bombardeia Gregor com maçãs. Uma se crava nas costas com tal força que <strong>ali permanece, apodrecendo na carne</strong> — a ferida que nunca cicatriza e inicia o declínio.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Leitura</div><div class=\"tipbody\">a maçã = violência paterna petrificada + punição edípica + eco da maçã bíblica (pecado e queda).</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "parte03-declinio-morte-e-renascimento": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">DIE VERWANDLUNG (1915)</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">A</span> <span class=\"bd\">METAMORFOSE</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Franz Kafka</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">1</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">A METAMORFOSE</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PARTE III: Declínio, Morte e Renascimento</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">A Arte como Último Laço</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">A</span>o ouvir Grete tocar violino, Gregor é tomado de emoção e se arrasta para a sala, fascinado, sentindo que a música o chama de volta ao humano. <strong>A alma resiste no corpo de bicho</strong> — e é justamente isso que o condena.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Símbolo</div><div class=\"tipbody\">o violino é a ponte para a humanidade perdida; o momento de quase-redenção que precipita o fim.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">2</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">A METAMORFOSE</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PARTE III: Declínio, Morte e Renascimento</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">Da Compaixão à Sentença</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">G</span>rete, antes cuidadora, completa o arco de menina a mulher e a juíza: declara que <strong>aquela criatura já não é Gregor e tem de sumir</strong>. Gregor escuta cada palavra — e, sem revolta, lhe dá razão.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Para refletir</div><div class=\"tipbody\">a frase de Grete mata Gregor mais que a maçã; o afeto vira repúdio.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">3</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">A METAMORFOSE</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PARTE III: Declínio, Morte e Renascimento</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">A Morte como Alívio</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">E</span>svaziado, ferido e faminto, Gregor recolhe-se ao quarto e morre ao amanhecer, ainda pensando na família com ternura. A faxineira acha o corpo seco e o descarta. <strong>A reação dos Samsa não é luto, mas alívio.</strong></p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Leitura</div><div class=\"tipbody\">a morte é a única saída do absurdo; Gregor a aceita — e nisso há uma estranha dignidade.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>04</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"ed\"><div class=\"ed-head\"><div class=\"ed-num\">4</div><div class=\"ed-meta\"><div class=\"ed-kicker\">A METAMORFOSE</div><div class=\"ed-rule\"></div><div class=\"ed-source\"><b>PARTE III: Declínio, Morte e Renascimento</b></div></div></div><h1 class=\"ed-title\">O Renascimento dos Vivos</h1><p class=\"ed-body\"><span class=\"dc\">L</span>ibertos, os Samsa despedem os hóspedes e saem num passeio de bonde ao campo. Ao sol, os pais notam que <strong>Grete desabrochou numa bela jovem</strong> em idade de casar. A vida segue, indiferente ao morto.</p><div class=\"ed-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><div class=\"tiptext\"><div class=\"tiplabel\">Ironia final</div><div class=\"tipbody\">a obra fecha não no luto, mas no futuro — Kafka nega a Gregor qualquer redenção dos vivos.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"]}}